snippet.title: Off The Cuff with Adam Banks-392-See Ya Next Year!
snippet.description:
Episode 392: Adam Banks and Amber Turner discuss the following in this episode: 

1.  The biggest News Stories of 2021 

2. John Madden dies 

3. Celebrity deaths in 2021 

4. The oldest celebrities that are still alive in 2021

5. How old would these celeberties be if they were still alive?

6.  Tubby Smith is returning to Coach at Rupp Arena after 24 years and is getting a banner. 

7. The biggest pop culture headlines of 2021


AND MORE!!
